      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/russian-finance-ministry-increase-deferred-daily-fx-purchases-2024-12-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯财政部周三表示，将在未来六周内增加延期外币和黄金购买量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/russian-finance-ministry-increase-deferred-daily-fx-purchases-2024-12-04/</guid>
